00:21.265 --> 00:26.192
You have that Shakespeare quote from The Tempest, which comes right after Dukedom Large Enough.

00:26.212 --> 00:29.135
At any rate, he tells the story.

00:29.175 --> 00:31.879
In those days, you know, they weren't selling books.

00:31.939 --> 00:34.442
People didn't queue up to buy books.

00:35.333 --> 00:47.465
He took a suitcase full of books and went to call on Hogan, who was a lawyer, and who had saved Mr. Doheny, whose library, his wife's library was auctioned in 87.

00:47.645 --> 00:49.087
From Tipar Dome.

00:49.107 --> 00:50.088
From Tipar Dome.

00:50.108 --> 00:53.411
He had saved Mr. Doheny from going to jail.

00:55.073 --> 01:01.339
